reviews.text:
Good food, decently priced restaurant.

Ordered the Deep fried pork cutlet, eel & egg bowl and it was quite good.

Their deep fry pork cutlet was not oily at all — which can be a turn off for me if oily.

Definitely worth a try if you around the area.
I normally avoid deep fried food and this was no different but prices are really cheap and my friends seem to enjoy the food. Definitely worth a try
Reasonably priced but very mediocre. The rice and curry katsu could have benefited from some extra ingredients as garnish..
I mistook it for another restaurant in Tokyo. My fault for not being more careful. It is still a decent restaurant serving Japanese meals like Tonkasu.
Nice Japanese Donburi restaurant with relatively low price

reviews.text:
Good food, decently priced restaurant.

Ordered the Deep fried pork cutlet, eel & egg bowl and it was quite good.

Their deep fry pork cutlet was not oily at all — which can be a turn off for me if oily.

Definitely worth a try if you around the area.

吉豕屋：主打吉列豬排、亦有炸蝦及雞排。
有加一服務費(10% service charges)。
味道還可以，就是不能天天吃呢。
新鮮即炸的豬扒飯，豬扒脆漿夠香脆。吃過多次仍能保持水準，值得一讚。不過，美中不足的是午餐時段仍要收加一服務費。
整體豬扒做得不錯，比其他日式豬扒飯便宜，中午午餐也要付加一服務費。
